  • Packages that use org.beiter.michael.db 
    Package Description
    org.beiter.michael.db
    Provides a classes to obtain a JDBC database connection, for instance from JNDI or from a connection pool.
    org.beiter.michael.db.propsbuilder
    Provides classes to build the properties required for the JDBC database connection management package.
